				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathrm{c}\left(t\right)=\left|\left(\text{1 - }\frac{t}{\text{Maxiter}}\right)\right|.$$\end{document}

Truong and Chou47 proposed a fuzzy adaptive time control mechanism to improve exploration and exploitation during the movement of the jellyfish, where the ocean current rate (OCR) and the jellyfish swarm rate (JSR) are inputs and the output is bar movement bar(t). The bar(t) is used to tune the time control function c(t), according to the following equation47.23ct=c(t-1)+bar(t-1),\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
